wiki.summary: (G)I-DLE “Queencard” song description on Melon Korean Music Platform: “Queencard” by (G)I-DLE is a vibrant celebration of self-love. The song underscores the importance of accepting oneself as they are, rather than focusing on external appearances. It brings to light the realization that genuine self-love embodies the real ‘Queencard’, as defined by (G)I-DLE. The song encourages listeners to embrace their individuality and cultivate self-love. Read more on Last.fm.
